ct\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"TokensProvider","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract14TokensProviderP"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BorderSemanticTokens","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic06BorderB6TokensP"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/allbordersemantictokensprovider"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider/borders":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/borders","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"borders","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provider of border semantic tokens to use for button borders"}],"fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"borders","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": any ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract31AllBorderSemanticTokensProviderP","text":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider\/borders"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"Theme Orange","abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for components with a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"control item"}]},{"text":" layout like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSSwitch","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioButton"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckboItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},